Name: Killing Trials
About the game: Killing Trials - Platform game about testing the survival of a small organism in difficult conditions among various traps. You play the role of a black spot, passing the test room. Avoid falling on the spikes, falling under the shots of stationary guns, sizzling lasers and much more.
